name: Dream #1: Bird-headed girl skateboarding
description: Now I am going through a very interesting period in my life: my dreams are very detailed, surreal. In the mornings I sometimes have a long time trying to figure out if what happened in the dream was reality or if it is reality here in my bed. Some images from dreams I write down.  This piece depicts a Bird-headed girl riding a skateboard. This is dream #1.
